    <item>
      <title>We Need a Social Scientist!</title>
      <link>https://Faculty-Job-Market-Collab.github.io/news/22-04-25-hiring/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://Faculty-Job-Market-Collab.github.io/news/22-04-25-hiring/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;In 2019-20 we ran a detailed survey to assess the faculty job market, collected applicant demographics, and expanded our data collection efforts to include social science researchers. However, as the collaboration was formed by biomedical researchers, we are now looking  an individual to lead the social science data analysis and manuscript writing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Submit an application (including: cover letter, CV, and writing sample) to
&lt;a href=&#34;njadav@midwestern.edu&#34;&gt;Nafisa Jadavji, PhD&lt;/a&gt; by &lt;strong&gt;April 30th, 2022&lt;/strong&gt;. Notification on May 15th 2022 to successful candidate, with a start date of June 1st 2022.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&#34;cta-group&#34;&gt;
  
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;https://docs.google.com/document/d/1fL28EQm8sJ7xxzZphgdLvQ6v2HawqFpIvdp_5Sxf8tE/edit&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34; class=&#34;btn btn-primary px-3 py-3&#34;&gt;Read the full job post.&lt;/a&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  
  
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;blockquote class=&#34;twitter-tweet&#34;&gt;&lt;p lang=&#34;en&#34; dir=&#34;ltr&#34;&gt;We are hiring a contract &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/hashtag/socialscientist?src=hash&amp;amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;#socialscientist&lt;/a&gt;, see below. We have exciting faculty job market data! Please retweet. &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/hashtag/humanities?src=hash&amp;amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;#humanities&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/hashtag/facultyjobmarket?src=hash&amp;amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;#facultyjobmarket&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/hashtag/academia?src=hash&amp;amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;#academia&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/hashtag/socialscience?src=hash&amp;amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;#socialscience&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/hashtag/AcademicChatter?src=hash&amp;amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;#AcademicChatter&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/hashtag/AcademicTwitter?src=hash&amp;amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;#AcademicTwitter&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/ACLS1919?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;@ACLS1919&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/BWFUND?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;@BWFUND&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/BWFPATH?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;@BWFPATH&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://t.co/4nI2RzYfpP&#34;&gt;https://t.co/4nI2RzYfpP&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://t.co/aDnjKOtNMv&#34;&gt;pic.twitter.com/aDnjKOtNMv&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&amp;mdash; Dr. Nafisa M. Jadavji ðŸ˜· (@nafisajadavji) &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/nafisajadavji/status/1516465301465882624?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;April 19, 2022&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
